title: TenZ responds after viral posts accuse Kyedae of cheating clarifies John Choi trip and calls rumors harmful
summary_full: TenZ addressed online rumors claiming Kyedae cheated on him with John Choi. He denied the claims, saying John is a shared friend and photos were taken out of context. He also denied donating bone marrow to Kyedae. Later, TenZ said esports helped him ignore online hate. Kyedae has not commented.
